short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Extracts thumbnails from a youtube video and allows user to download the thumbnails

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension allows users to easily download a thumbnail for a YouTube video. Simply click on the extension's icon while on a page with a YouTube video, a new tab will open containing the images for download.

Have any issues? Want to add new features? Checkout the GitHub here - https://github.com/ghughes13/csl-youtube-thumbnail-extractor
